    transliteration: "kathaṃ na jñeyam asmābhiḥ pāpād asmān nivartitum\nkula-kṣhaya-kṛtaṃ doṣhaṃ prapaśhyadbhir janārdana",
    translation: "O Janardana, why should we, who can see the crime in destroying a family, engage in these acts of sin?",
