        <p><strong>2. Loss of Identity:</strong> He uses the word <em>utsādyante</em> (devastated/wiped out). Without <em>kula-dharma</em>, people lose their sense of identity, duty, and belonging. They become a "rootless" population without a guiding philosophy.</p>

